{"tid":1557471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得我地贏唔到既原因係因為主流有政治潔癖？","createTime":"2019-09-10T06:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T10:49:56.000Z","uid":4236,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3ce85b9dcd1c634e95187b342d229a8603082b","tid":1557471,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:28:37.000Z","msg":"我地依家對暴力係無潔癖 <br />\n但太固執覺得唔可以靠人地 要靠自己 要用香港人呢個身份贏<br />\n但呢個做法其實極幼稚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地軍隊又無咩都無<br />\n理得你投靠美國定英國定其他國家<br />\n總之贏到就得啦 贏左個歷史就係由我地去寫<br />\n睇下d人 講緊我地手足<br />\n<br />\n美國？ 不了 我地中國人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反共產黨only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n獨立？ 不了 我地要一國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得自己中國人就不如唔好抗爭啦 大中華膠有咩用<br />\n覺得自己係香港人 就唔該利用美國到盡啦 反正佢都係利用緊我地<br />\n一人一支美國旗 比位人地幫我地好過啦<br />\n總之邊個有勢力既企出黎幫我地 我地就投靠邊個<br />\n萬大事都應該贏左再考慮 唔應該執著點去做<br />\n正義係由勝利者去定義 唔係loser<br />\n<br />\n預左負評 依家主流個做法都係太天真<br />\nps 唔知係咪應該用政治潔癖呢個term"},{"pid":"4186b558fa55b07a18a1079437a97f1588bde476","tid":1557471,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249b49b6db38b5d286c8853368113718e8c24eb0","tid":1557471,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4488eaff47f709985e6c66659e7503408f8ae1c9","tid":1557471,"u